Class SchemaTabbedPane

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component

    public class SchemaTabbedPane
extends javax.swing.JTabbedPane
    SchemaTabbedPane represents the container of SchemaTab tabs. It is a specialization of JTabbedPane.

    Viktor

    • Method Detail

      • add

        public void add(TableNode node)
        Method for adding content to the SchemaTabbedPane. Content is passed through TableNode parameter. From the node the Table is extracted and table content is used in building the SchemaTab content. Allows only unique occurrences of tabs, if tab is already present only focus is set.
        Parameters:
        node - - TableNode is a specific node from SchemaTree

      • add

        public void add(Table table)
        Method for adding content to the SchemaTabbedPane. Content is passed through Table parameter, table content is used in building the SchemaTab content. Allows only unique occurrences of tabs, if tab is already present only focus is set.
        Parameters:
        table - - Table

      • TabWithCodePresentPosition

        public int TabWithCodePresentPosition(java.lang.String code)
        Method for checking whether JTabbedPane extension SchemaTabbedPane contains specific extension of JTab - SchemaTab. Tab is uniquely identified by its Table code.
        Parameters:
        code - Table unique identifier, code field
        Returns:
        Index if the tab is present, -1 if not found

      • changeLanguage

        public void changeLanguage(java.util.ResourceBundle rb)
        Method for changing the display language of the SchemaTabbedPane and currently displayed content of active and opened instances of SchemaTab.
        Parameters:
        rb - Resource bundle containing the translation with appropriate codes
